{"tid":1057846,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"委臨時總統要求頒佈緊急狀態","createTime":"2019-03-12T07:06:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-12T07:06:19.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b68208cc3adb2201729bef9e9136674a94480b34","tid":1057846,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T07:06:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190312/20631216\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190312%2F20631216&d=%2BklfNN7Cu7rnXjHLlXUq6FSbRuvIKfaxuJHhOs3YWJk%3D&h=8ced1ca9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190312%2F20631216&h=d4151924\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190312/20631216</a><br />\n<br />\n委臨時總統要求頒佈緊急狀態<br />\n<br />\n2019-03-12<br />\n國際新聞<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190312/large/12wh103p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190312%2Flarge%2F12wh103p.jpg&h=d8b345b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n委內瑞拉停電危機至前日踏入第四天，僅有零星地區恢復電源，馬杜羅政府至今未交代因由，臨時總統瓜伊多（圖中）昨日國會特別會議上要求國家進入緊急狀態。<br />\n<br />\n前日在當地一間侷促的酒店房間接受美國有線新聞網絡訪問時，瓜伊多稱停電期間有17人因為缺乏電力而遭「謀殺」；他並駁斥馬杜羅政府指控美國的說法，「說停電是美國網絡攻擊造成很荒謬」，因為國家電力系統本來就已老舊，目前境況「不是因為颶風，也不是因為海嘯，而是這個腐敗政府太不濟兼沒效率，不理人民死活」。瓜伊多又說正跟德國、日本、哥倫比亞和巴西等多國商議，並從多邊機構籌集了15億美元可供應付委國各項公共服務。<br />\n<br />\n路透社"}]}